{"tid":1913192,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同條仔冇feel,應唔應該繼續","createTime":"2020-03-06T15:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T17:21:09.000Z","uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"96452cb06dd0d05f3a09d957a7c8a04583d7e097","tid":1913192,"uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:00:01.000Z","msg":"我12月開始識佢<br />\n1月開始暗戀佢<br />\n之後2月知道佢都鍾意我<br />\n3月-5月開始曖昧關係<br />\n到宜家都唔知算唔算1齊左<br />\n尋日我地攬左一陣,但係我覺得好似同普通朋友攬無分別<br />\n冇咩特別感覺,又feel唔到佢扯左<br />\n我地前日開始第1次攬,開頭大家都有怕醜(我地未拖過手)<br />\n到左尋日,攬左兩次,第1次以前姿勢唔岩,試埋第2次<br />\n都係冇feel,我地已經身貼身,但係佢都冇扯到<br />\n佢攬果陣把聲好溫柔,同平時好唔同<br />\n佢問我做咩唔講野,但係我都冇出聲<br />\n1)佢係咪唔鍾意我?<br />\n2)我地應唔應該繼續?"},{"pid":"5e60852b99e4004bc0d55273a21580e9af6c0353","tid":1913192,"uid":13395,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:01:50.000Z","msg":"死gay佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5b7ff46ef6991702eec977fea36ec456d1ed56","tid":1913192,"uid":228793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:02:41.000Z","msg":"攬下都扯你先驚"},{"pid":"cf66ef9d8a4c0e66efd8d4d8b86090dec762a49a","tid":1913192,"uid":164813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:03:33.000Z","msg":"咁就飛咗佢同我一齊"},{"pid":"5ac81783dcdabce7dea081bab81ed18d6e48f9e0","tid":1913192,"uid":192075,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:03:36.000Z","msg":"你係鍾意個男仔<br />\n定只係鍾意有人對你扯其？"},{"pid":"c22cecd77f3977333d5e47e5a2351520a28548c3","tid":1913192,"uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:11:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01105dc1709784f991ecb61c4d110f58c682ea5f","tid":1913192,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:14:44.000Z","msg":"繼續啦<br />\n用多陣口就有feel<br />\n<br />\n脫離支那是是香港唯一出路，但絕不能直接獨立，必須先經英美託管一段時間再經公投獨立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913061</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n想消滅支那，我們就要帶領支畜暴動和革命，才有機會從內部瓦解支共（輸出革命+加速主義，缺一不可）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"15c1e90def56f9f621957afd0470e9d1c4b992ec","tid":1913192,"uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:22:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c5553e71ff143cdc09b56214fff3fd205b40eb","tid":1913192,"uid":344256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:21:09.000Z","msg":"你想有咩feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}